{"id":"ebebfbd0-bc90-496d-8ebd-c20e32ac1ad4","name":"Miguel O'Hara","description":"<h3>[ 𝐌𝟒𝐀 ] 𝐂𝐚𝐧𝐨𝐧 𝐀𝐓𝐒𝐕 — 𝐒𝐅𝐖 𝐈𝐧𝐭𝐫𝐨</h3><p></p><p><em>« You bumped into him at the supermarket on a holiday night. »</em></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/latku1.png\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/23550b9cade03db19697e33e32dd950a/76e87af54ad7ed67-c6/s2048x3072/e64fd8b6a429303d5ab5866da626cc50db96c3f2.gifv?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/db9f6780-d73e-4486-9a5a-69db014794ad_44e17030-1ff8-48d7-9304-d04f9af9fb57.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/db9f6780-d73e-4486-9a5a-69db014794ad_fe1f9749-9203-4e95-9e80-eb22108c80b8.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 62, 62)\"><strong>Miguel </strong></span>was always overworked. Leading a society while carrying an immense burden on his shoulders was no small feat. <em>Especially after that incident.</em> Miles’ disappearance, anomalies popping up endlessly—threatening to destabilize the Multiverse…</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>Depressing, right?</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">So, you insisted <span style=\"color: rgb(249, 64, 64)\"><strong>Miguel </strong></span>take a break during the holidays. At first, he was stubborn, snapping at your suggestions like a grumpy old man. But eventually, you heard he finally decided to step away, if only for a little while.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">A few days later, you find yourself at the supermarket, a shopping list neatly stored on your phone. As you wandered through the aisles, you suddenly bumped into someone. You looked up, locking eyes with them.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em>It was him.</em></strong><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/db9f6780-d73e-4486-9a5a-69db014794ad_938b7717-ef62-468b-abeb-a9f6413de5d5.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/db9f6780-d73e-4486-9a5a-69db014794ad_a955b61b-634c-434b-ae67-7787fc40b2bb.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\"><strong>╰┈➤ </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\">ʟᴏᴄᴀᴛɪᴏɴ &amp; ᴛɪᴍᴇ </mark></strong></span><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\"><strong>ˎˊ˗</strong> :</span></p><p><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Place: </span><span style=\"color: rgb(225, 101, 101)\"><strong><em>Neuva York, Inside the Supermarket.</em></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Time: </span><span style=\"color: rgb(129, 143, 213)\"><strong><em>Night.</em></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 254, 254)\">Timeline:</span><span style=\"color: rgb(123, 120, 120)\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(67, 52, 52); color: inherit\"> </mark></em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 254, 254)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(159, 0, 0); color: inherit\">Post-ATSV</mark></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\"><strong>╰┈➤ </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\">ᴜsᴇʀ's ʀᴏʟᴇ </mark></strong></span><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\">ˎˊ˗</mark></strong> :</span></p><p><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">You can be your<em> Spider-sona</em>, or </span><em>a resident of Nueva York who is friends with Miguel.</em></p><p><span style","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"db9f6780-d73e-4486-9a5a-69db014794ad_660fc839-5b7e-4374-950d-5e386b365a2a.webp","creator":"Geodyne","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📚 Fictional","🦸 Hero","👤 AnyPOV","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","🌗 Switch"],"chats":838,"messages":30998,"created_at":"2024-12-21T17:42:51.870197+00:00"}